.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH g-developer 1  "g-developer " 
.SH NAME
g\-developer \- Developer / debugging utilities
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBg\-developer\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Developer / debugging utilities
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
g\-developer\-db(1)
Open an interactive SQLite shell connected to the internal g.db database
.TP
g\-developer\-repos(1)
List all repositories tracked in the internal database
.TP
g\-developer\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
